1. *Pokušavamo* da shvatimo koncept.(We are trying to understand the concept.)
2. Oni su *pokušavali* da prevaziđu prepreke.(They were trying to overcome obstacles.)
3. *Pokušavamo* da sprečimo nastanak problema.(We are trying to prevent the occurrence of problems.)
4. Nastojala je da *pokuša* da ostvari svoje snove.(She was trying to achieve her dreams.)
5. *Pokušali* smo da izbegnemo sudar.(We tried to avoid a collision.)
6. Oni su *pokušavali* da odgovore na pitanje.(They were trying to answer the question.)